articles.title: Jakarta governor outlines plans to ease congestion in city
articles.content: In an exclusive interview with CNA, Jakarta governor Pramono Anung outlines how he plans to tackle the city's crippling traffic gridlock. But will austerity measures introduced by the national government stand in his way?
